@startuml
' Định nghĩa các thành phần
actor User
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong)" as Kong
participant "Service ABC" as ABC
participant "Service XYZ" as XYZ

' Luồng Request
User -> Kong: Gửi Request
activate Kong

Kong -> ABC: Forward Request
activate ABC

ABC -> XYZ: Gọi API / Lấy dữ liệu
activate XYZ

' Luồng Response
XYZ --> ABC: Trả về Response
deactivate XYZ

ABC --> Kong: Trả về Response
deactivate ABC

Kong --> User: Final Response
deactivate Kong
@enduml
